ink that would steer a great deal of capital away from coal stocks, but rea=
lly BlackRock doesn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0decide where its money goes and its mone=
y keeps going to coal stocks.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And in fact l=
ast year <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24428997.=
