ve moves to preserve their massive wealth, but whatever man:</p><blockquote=
><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Another member of the group is Kate Marie, a =
59-year-old healthcare technology consultant in Sydney, who dipped into the=
 world of crypto futures in early 2020 after her business was dissolved ove=
r a dispute.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">After reading =E2=80=9CTrend T=
rading for Dummies,=E2=80=9D and watching YouTube tutorials, Ms. Marie said=
