ther begin to slide, he clicked the app to exit his positions, take losses =
and move on. But the Binance app on his phone was frozen and nothing would =
click, he said. He kept trying for about an hour.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16=
px 0;">Then he received a message saying he had been liquidated as his loss=
